{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "b10313f6-5d75-41b3-a39f-1d75b6c1a16e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b10313f6-5d75-41b3-a39f-1d75b6c1a16e@1.pkg/1772597662201/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597662884", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b10313f6-5d75-41b3-a39f-1d75b6c1a16e@1.pkg/1772597662201/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597662884"}, "identifier": "b10313f6-5d75-41b3-a39f-1d75b6c1a16e", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查民法典的道德体现。</p>\n\n<p>A:社会主义核心价值观倡导友善，民法典规定自愿实施紧急救助行为造成受助人损害的救助人不承担民事责任，有利于鼓励人们践行友善，融入了社会主义核心价值观，故符合题意.</p>\n\n<p>B:这一规定彰显的是助人为乐的中华传统美德，而不是城市守信的传统美德。</p>\n\n<p>C:这一规定有利于保护救助人的合法权益，鼓励人们积极救助他人，符合公平正义，不应该修改。</p>\n\n<p>D:“消除社会矛盾”说法过于绝对，错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）“因自愿实施紧急救助行为造成受助人损害的，救助人不承担民事责任。”民法典的这一规定（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）“因自愿实施紧急救助行为造成受助人损害的，救助人不承担民事责任。”民法典的这一规定（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b10313f6-5d75-41b3-a39f-1d75b6c1a16e@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755144277888", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": []